{"tid":1032068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"離奇墮樓失憶空姐3年後露面 喪失智力容貌大變","createTime":"2019-02-22T06:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T07:50:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1267cb87a114ec995add769d4020f44fcbdc4884","tid":1032068,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190222/_2019022210430640461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190222%2F_2019022210430640461.jpg&h=648757ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川航空空姐陳麗丹2015年5月在三亞從酒店7樓墮下，墮樓原因一直是個謎，引人關注。3年後，陳麗丹面對鏡頭受訪，家人稱她事後失去記憶，智力低下，關於墮樓情形仍記不起。警方結案為自殺，其父稱仍想尋找真相。<br />\n<br />\n2015年5月26日，四川航空公司空姐陳麗丹及機組人員出差三亞，住在公司安排的三亞玉海酒店。凌晨，陳麗丹離奇從7樓墮下，身受重傷。「川航空姐三亞跳樓事件」一度震驚全國，引起關注。近日，現年26歲的陳麗丹首次公開露面接受訪問，鏡頭前的她不僅失去昔日的美顏，連當年墮樓的細節也記不起。警方當日結案為自殺，但其父陳勝昌則表示，女兒不可能為情自殺，他認為女兒與男友關係非常要好，不太可能那樣做，仍想找出女兒墮樓真相。<br />\n<br />\n悲劇發生了3年，陳麗丹記憶力衰退，連當年墮樓的經過和原因無法記，就連自己做過空姐也仿佛印象模糊。當年悲劇發生之後，她大腦受損、牙齒脫落，臉部毀容，失去記憶，更昏迷了3個月。頭部鑲了300多顆鋼釘和多塊鋼板，如今容貌雖然修復了，但整個臉都變了型，但被問及自己的現時與昔日的樣貌分別，陳麗丹充滿自信地表示「沒有太大分別，感覺是一樣的」、「現在樣貌一樣好看」。其母表示陳麗丹的智力有衰退的徵兆。<br />\n<br />\n當年傳媒報道，陳麗丹墮樓原因有多種說法，有傳與情感轇轕有關、有傳遭性侵、被下藥產生幻覺等，但由於陳麗丹已經失憶，墮樓原因都未能夠證實，可能永遠成謎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/939175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F939175&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLUxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=51c9fa28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F939175&h=89a9e75d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/939175</a>"},{"pid":"096e40901294d4b2cea93561f88327141f0d9885","tid":1032068,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"左邊明顯ps過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85f3f60f0b496db0788a011458d9325880043cf","tid":1032068,"uid":224452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSZUnxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSZUnxv.jpg&h=bd82aaf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R30o0jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR30o0jd.jpg&h=0b7249b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07828f870703789dfac86e76962e0acbf2ac0c3e","tid":1032068,"uid":112498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"屌你.. 兩個人黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787bcdab3fa48ef77bc0c00ee2f939f4d1a75266","tid":1032068,"uid":190604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"卸妝同p圖前後"},{"pid":"577e79492304c6c68d4aed2c1c8305917c877bae","tid":1032068,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"被問及自己的現時與昔日的樣貌分別，陳麗丹充滿自信地表示「沒有太大分別，感覺是一樣的」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「現在樣貌一樣好看」。其母表示陳麗丹的智力有衰退的徵兆。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d978bb9fd960ca75b91910e18010c9915dcbb3","tid":1032068,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"577e79492304c6c68d4aed2c1c8305917c877bae","tid":1032068,"uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"被問及自己的現時與昔日的樣貌分別，陳麗丹充滿自信地表示「沒有太大分別，感覺是一樣的」、<span style=\"color: red;\">「現在樣貌一樣好看」。其母表示陳麗丹的智力有衰退的徵兆。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi